Identify and measure mobilization factors.
On the contrary, the managerial revolution necessary for the proper functioning of modern enterprises presupposes the adoption of the ultimate vision of human behavior.
It consists in incorporating a basic observation into all management intentions and practices: Commitments to the company will only be possible for employees if they appear to be a clear means of achieving their dreams, ambitions and projects.
Currently, only studies of Motivational Functional Analysis deal with this concept of employee motivation.
